When you select it a region on a track your selection will snap to a user defined grid value.


[[File:Ableton Live track selection snap to grid lines.png]]


To change this value or enable or disable it, right click on the audio track. A menu will appear.The bottom section of this menu will list different grid value options.

[[File:Ableton Live grid snap menu.png]]


The grid options are

*'''Adaptive grid''' - This changes the grid based on zoom level and gives you five different choices from "widest" to "narrowest"., 

*'''Fixed grid''' - This is a set grid value and a list of time divisions are gives from 8 bars to 1/32

*'''Off''' - This turns off the grid value.



